    <h2>AMC Contracts — What They Cost & What's Included</h2>

    <p>An Annual Maintenance Contract (AMC) is a pre-paid service agreement with an equipment dealer or third-party service provider. For commercial kitchen equipment, AMCs typically range from <strong>₹5,000 to ₹25,000 per year</strong> per piece of equipment, depending on the type, brand, and coverage level.</p>

    <h3>Types of AMC</h3>

    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>AMC Type</th>
          <th>Typical Cost (per year)</th>
          <th>What's Included</th>
          <th>What's NOT Included</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Basic / Non-Comprehensive</strong></td>
          <td>₹5,000 – ₹10,000</td>
          <td>2–4 preventive maintenance visits per year, cleaning, calibration, inspection</td>
          <td>Parts, major repairs, emergency calls</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Comprehensive</strong></td>
          <td>₹10,000 – ₹18,000</td>
          <td>Everything in Basic + parts replacement (wear items), priority emergency response</td>
          <td>Compressor, heating elements (may be extra), accidental damage</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
