        <div class="faq-a">
          <p>Start with your equipment dealer or authorised distributor — they maintain technician networks and stock genuine parts. If your dealer is unresponsive, try local bakery owner WhatsApp groups for recommendations. Platforms like IndiaMart list commercial equipment service providers by city. Avoid generic appliance repair services from apps — most specialise in household appliances and lack experience with commercial equipment. BakeDesk can also connect you with verified technicians in your area.</p>
